"reviewcomment":"Great find in Boston - it&#39;s a chain so I will preface with that, in the fact that I rarely visit or rate chains with 4-5 stars but Hillstone deserves it. I have visited them in multiple states and have never been let down. I wish there were 1/2 stars because I would absolutely give out 4.5, but I am a little stingy with my 5&#39;s.<br><br>Service is always excellent, decor is impeccable, bar area is always busy with a fun vibe and the dining rooms are dim &amp; sultry. I love their steak with a good glass of wine or champagne - it&#39;s definitely my idea of a perfect dinner. The husband has tried their ribs, fish &amp; burgers all of which he really enjoyed. <br><br>The portions are large, so you can easily enjoy some apps and share an entree (which they happily split for a minimal charge) and have a little room for something sweet. <br><br>I personally suggest sitting at the bar, or outside if possible. Those are the best seats in the house for people watching, fast service and ambiance. <br><br>Definitely a go-to spot when we are staying downtown or in Cambridge.",
