"reviewcomment":"Though I haven&#39;t been to the actual restaurant in quite a while, I&#39;ve been enjoying Sweet Chili more often than not -- thanks to those folks over at Seamless (their discount emails always get me). <br><br>But I don&#39;t mind, because not only do I get to order in (whether it&#39;s because I&#39;m treating myself to pad thai while working, or because I don&#39;t want to cook while I am binging on Netflix and Hulu...), but I also get a spectacular deal each time I order. The delivery guy (same one each time) is also a very cheerful fella, so that&#39;s always nice. :-)<br><br>I never feel like I ever get gypped here. I get a decent amount of food for my $ -- even (especially?) with the lunch specials. They&#39;re &#34;smaller&#34; portions, but they come with little apps (Thai rolls and such) and they&#39;re very reasonably priced. Case in point: my gra pao lunch combo yesterday actually fed me for both lunch and linner (LOL, OF COURSE I ATE ANOTHER DINNER)... all for less than $15 (incl. $2 delivery fee and $2 tip). And they run lunch specials until FOUR P.M. -- huzzah!<br><br>Anyway, I&#39;m a big fan... whether I eat in or eat out, Sweet Chili&#39;s my Thai place of choice in Arlington.",
