"reviewcomment":"Martin&#39;s Coffee Shop is one of my favorite breakfast destinations in all of Boston. This is your typical hole-in-the-wall diner that serves up the usuals at at very affordable price. However, just because they serve ordinary diner food does not mean they don&#39;t do it extraordinarily well. It is located in the quaint little shopping plaza of Brookline Village and is easy to miss if you&#39;re not looking for it. From the outside, it doesn&#39;t look like much. However, the constant line forming out of their door should automatically tell you that this place is a winner.<br><br>Check out my blog (complete with pictures and childish humor) for the full review! <br><br><a href='/redir?url=http%3A%2F%2Fthesuchef.org%2F2013%2F10%2F28%2Fmartins-coffee-shop-to-go%2F&amp;s=0bd872d8195b370b1bf9940242eefa6deda288409211c4aa573fb52ed1266fd4' target='_blank' rel='nofollow'>thesuchef.org/2013/10/28…</a>",
